ActInternational Bridges and Tunnels Act
SubjectAcquisition of the Sprague's Falls, Baring and Salmon Falls international railway bridges by the Woodland Rail LLC and their operation by the Eastern Maine Railway Company
PrecisOrder approving the acquisition of the SPRAGUE'S FALLS, BARING AND SALMON FALLS international railway bridges that span the St. Croix River between St. Stephen, New Brunswick and Baileyville, Maine, by the Woodland Rail LLC and their operation by the Eastern Maine Railway Company.
